91618_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F191618_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1c849e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/191628_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F191628_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=24bf1524&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81eb6cbee2682261e0ed434eaccef71d99397c32","tid":496092,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"香港人的社運總是美好的，青春的，浪漫的"},{"pid":"9b3076f0e0127f80fac772ea00325ce971c87862","tid":496092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做得好！關鍵時刻築成人牆保護立法會，免受暴徒衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛優美開始</span>"},{"pid":"d9fc055f7b550358aa22a74dd13a3b63128fddb1","tid":496092,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做得好！關鍵時刻築成人牆保護立法會，免受暴徒衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛優美開始</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/192408_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F192408_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f