":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宣傳力度仲係好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cca6fc6598df62071d1fa2ba3f403d540f23699","tid":496092,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/194135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F194135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dad7cc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#終極一戰】修改議事規則已經殺到埋身，我哋一定唔會坐以待斃，議會內必定會用盡一切方法去阻止，而議會外更加需要市民支持。由今晚開始，民主派將會舉行包圍立法會行動，紮營留守立法會廣場。希望市民能夠到場支持，務求集結民氣，推倒修改議案！<br />\n<br />\n包圍立法會行動詳情：<br />\n11/12(一) 18：00 開始紮營留守<br />\n12/12(二) 19：00 分享會<br />\n13/12(三) 18：00 集會包圍立法會<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n📣支持民主黨工作： <a href=\"http://goo.gl/70jmS2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F70jmS2&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b1d64487\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/70jmS2</a><br />\n💪🏻成為民主黨義工： <a href=\"http://goo.gl/l0IIVL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fl0IIVL&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=261a91f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/l0IIVL</a><br />\n📃立即加入民主黨： <a href=\"http://goo.gl/Ooc5K4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FOoc5K4&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=815c200a\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/Ooc5K4</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nFacebook： <a href=\"http://fb.com/thedphk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fthedphk&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8a1e4971\" target=\"_blank\">fb.com/thedphk</a><br />\nYoutube Channel ： <a href=\"http://youtube.com/user/dphkdphk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fuser%2Fdphkdphk&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b1e05240\" target=\"_blank\">youtube.com/user/dphkdphk</a><br />\nWebsite： <a href=\"http://www.dphk.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dphk.org&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f12f8bdc\" target=\"_blank\">www.dphk.org</a>"},{"pid":"98704ee1817cbfede9f7db9eb6d95601d10fd543","tid":496092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泛民今紮營圍立會　通宵<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">留守至後天</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係無論點, 後日都散<br />\n<br />\n原來捍衛議會權力係有時限？<br />\n<br />\n時限一到, 放棄, 去意大利HONEYMOON鳥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你班友個個月袋數十萬薪資, 都設限72小時<br />\n<br />\n我no paid既, 不如返屋企冬眠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c9a5ab6bad9427c1a1ca236b5e1547a05c6fe9","tid":496092,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母賣完香港貓哭老鼠"},{"pid":"cffb5cdae6a27ef700e0921d51133324041aa8d5","tid":496092,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:46:26.000Z","msg":"民主黨屌晒你地老母"},{"pid":"f362c96be314707e252bf94b21faf83035478124","tid":496092,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"一陣保安黑警清場咪齊齊bbq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039aa655656ac94451503c63df59d0b9b1a12f67","tid":496092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/191007_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F191007_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2c294f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/191012_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F191012_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=73bb1503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［終極一戰］<br />\n12月11日：晚上接近7:00:金鐘立法會示威區內聚集了一班泛民主派議員進駐紮營，目的是反對修改議事規則。<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">現場所見到場支持的市民寥寥可數。</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家一定唔記得社民連上次寸青政平日放工拖馬得300人啦?<br />\n<br />\n佢現場有無300?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327e4a1d7307d8a88a7e9320c25712fa60da1e0e","tid":496092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母賣完香港貓哭老鼠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胡志偉兩星期前先講過, 23條立法OK<br />\n<br />\n有諮詢就得, 民主黨就會投讚成<br />\n<br />\n今日又話, 唔去食風就會過23條<br />\n<br />\n精神分裂?"},{"pid":"3703e8c9fd37477cf7e6ed369123d9077564ed07","tid":496092,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一陣保安黑警清場咪齊齊bbq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0059aef811dbc6b69ce61615df0b8110698ea43","tid":496092,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"其實無架啦<br />\n至從928同魚蛋之後，發現原來班撚人最鐘意篤灰<br />\n最有行動力個班已經唔會再出黎<br />\n泛民豬仔要返工更加唔會黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加埋岩岩先有關鍵一席同建制大合照，點俾到信心人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次改完議事規則泛民就officially 無哂作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再含乜投票都無意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb35bd0d139c59e187746e5f3b8d438e757148a","tid":496092,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"終極一戰？收皮啦屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07d3d7a35b58a1ec808a437343063300d8a0540","tid":496092,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fbe4192d148f6cef8be82a23a3cd4f32203dca","tid":496092,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T12:00:01.000Z","msg":"屌 成日做埋晒啲門面嘢<br />\n有時間不如諗下點dumb down啲政治爭拗<br />\n招攬下對家啲廢老同新腥簡人好過啦<br />\n圍威喂有閪用咩，而家呢啲新聞根本無人知無人理<br />\n見到標題碌都碌唔切，搞大咗都只會覺得你搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01934c58e8f0de900948c4711c79ed16a993044","tid":496092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終極一戰？收皮啦屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有限時<br />\n<br />\n戰至後日, 就鐵定收工<br />\n<br />\n大家都要聖誕放假出外玩啦, 係咪?<br />\n<br />\n泛民班友唔係BOOK好晒酒店機票？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c434208b89be00e000e0f62c1915e8d500a147","tid":496092,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>終極一戰？收皮啦屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有限時<br />\n<br />\n戰至後日, 就鐵定收工<br />\n<br />\n大家都要聖誕放假出外玩啦, 係咪?<br />\n<br />\n泛民班友唔係BOOK好晒酒店機票？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n楊大狀要去度蜜月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9ffcb7ffd95c30dcbb9b5501f8e30153fbaaee","tid":496092,"uid":114123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/185802_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F185802_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8cb8e532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會後天續審修改立法會《議事規則》，預料最快本周完成審議。建制派多項修改建議被指閹割立法會職能，民主派力挽狂瀾，今晚6時起開始紮營包圍立法會，現任和被取消資格議員均會現身，呼籲市民今晚起到立法會外打氣，後天則會舉辦集會。人民力量議員陳志全指，由於要留守作戰，防止《議事規則》修訂順利通過，民主派後天大會不會貿然衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n上周審議修改《議事規則》期間，民主派議員多次中斷會議，於主席台前示威。<br />\n<br />\n立法會後天召開大會，先處理有關《議事規則》修訂的中止待續議案，之後便將正式踏入審議《議事規則》的修訂，每位議員面對逾百項修訂，卻僅得15分鐘發言。<br />\n民主派會議召集人莫乃光昨稱，由於將進入關鍵階段，加上留意到上周四已有不少巿民關注並出席立法會外的集會，故決定更早讓巿民參與行動表態，今晚民主派將會在公民廣場外紮營，不同黨派、現任和被取消資格議員及支持者，都會在該地守候到後天會議來臨。莫希望巿民明白，修改《議事規則》將嚴重影響立法會運作和監察政府的權力。<br />\n香港本土立法會議員毛孟靜指，今晚展開包圍立法會行動，巿民6時可到場聲援打氣，議員會向巿民解釋今次憲政危機。<br />\n人民力量立法會議員陳志全批評，今次建制派和「吹黑哨」的立法會主席梁君彥試圖快刀斬亂麻修改《議事規則》，故他希望更多巿民關注事件，預料民主派四大板塊中，有人會通宵留守。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳志全預告抗爭升級</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有消息指，立法會主席梁君彥將會趕走稍後於大會審議《議事規則》期間衝擊主席台的議員，陳志全指，考慮到一旦民主派議員被趕走，只餘下建制派議員在議會，屆時變相令所有《議事規則》修訂「舉手便通過」，所以他們要力保留在議會內，不會貿然衝擊。但陳志全預告，議會之內的抗爭行動可能會升級；毛孟靜亦指出，不便透露議會內抗爭對策，否則對方會有所防備。<br />\n莫乃光昨則譴責有消息指建制派計劃利用報警等恐嚇手段，阻止民主派捍衞立法會尊嚴，以及令立法會不被矮化，「既然佢哋（建制派）覺得立法會唔係議政場地，佢哋根本唔應該再喺立法會入面，亦無履行巿民畀佢哋嘅責任」。<br />\n公民黨黨魁楊岳橋昨稱今次修改《議事規則》，猶如一場建制派人數佔優勢的球賽，甚至擔當「球證」角色的梁君彥都屬建制陣營，令建制派可決定何時通過修訂，民主派只能在有限空間盡力拖延，「做得幾多得幾多」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171211/20241005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F20241005&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2475f685\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F20241005&h=e9f818a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171211/20241005</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劇本已經寫好<br />\n<br />\n1.大叫可恥當升左終<br />\n2.係電視機下比人抬出會議廳<br />\n3.修改議事規則最後通過<br />\n4.民主派開記招，流曬馬尿話今日係民主最黑暗一日，然後話日後仲有好多場仗要打，搬曬d高鐵，23條出來<br />\n5.記招最後就會話會繼續監察政府<br />\n6.動員社運KOL,黃絲，大中華膠去幫飯民去污名化 (例如黎則奮，細黃伯，區家麟)，內容不外乎懶感性中二病文章，例子有&rdquo;.....殊死決戰&rdquo;，&rdquo;時代選中我們走在一起&rdquo;<br />\n7.和理非香港人一呼百應，感謝佢地既付出，邊個唔認同就會批鬥佢地，理由不外乎&rdquo;獨立呀&rdquo;，&rdquo;勇武呀&rdquo;，&rdquo;從政一定要知所進退&rdquo;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 8.如常繼續返工</span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3068c870d906e57febdfc72654b2376031faf50f","tid":496092,"uid":70238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母賣完香港貓哭老鼠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胡志偉兩星期前先講過, 23條立法OK<br />\n<br />\n有諮詢就得, 民主黨就會投讚成<br />\n<br />\n今日又話, 唔去食風就會過23條<br />\n<br />\n精神分裂?</blockquote><br />\n屌，真係以為謊話講一千次就變事實。23條只需要簡單多數就可通過，跟本和修改議事規則無關!"},{"pid":"e1bdef9535e57c899606554c0a23e5ce129b0082","tid":496092,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母賣完香港貓哭老鼠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胡志偉兩星期前先講過, 23條立法OK<br />\n<br />\n有諮詢就得, 民主黨就會投讚成<br />\n<br />\n今日又話, 唔去食風就會過23條<br />\n<br />\n精神分裂?</blockquote><br />\n屌，真係以為謊話講一千次就變事實。23條只需要簡單多數就可通過，跟本和修改議事規則無關!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前夠話關健一席(缺席)就可以阻到改議事規則"},{"pid":"5f5ad3b3d4696f4dc1300566a7a108b32227b133","tid":496092,"uid":32938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"多撚餘 唔改議事規則D野咪一樣過到<br />\n係班垃圾泛民少左機會做show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8983d24352368196bb8a4ed2476e89c62439c3bd","tid":496092,"uid":64948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T00:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/194135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F194135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dad7cc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#終極一戰】修改議事規則已經殺到埋身，我哋一定唔會坐以待斃，議會內必定會用盡一切方法去阻止，而議會外更加需要市民支持。由今晚開始，民主派將會舉行包圍立法會行動，紮營留守立法會廣場。希望市民能夠到場支持，務求集結民氣，推倒修改議案！<br />\n<br />\n包圍立法會行動詳情：<br />\n11/12(一) 18：00 開始紮營留守<br />\n12/12(二) 19：00 分享會<br />\n13/12(三) 18：00 集會包圍立法會<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n📣支持民主黨工作： <a href=\"http://goo.gl/70jmS2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F70jmS2&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b1d64487\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/70jmS2</a><br />\n💪🏻成為民主黨義工： <a href=\"http://goo.gl/l0IIVL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fl0IIVL&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=261a91f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/l0IIVL</a><br />\n📃立即加入民主黨： <a href=\"http://goo.gl/Ooc5K4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FOoc5K4&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=815c200a\" target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/Ooc5K4</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nFacebook： <a href=\"http://fb.com/thedphk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fthedphk&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8a1e4971\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/thedphk</a><br />\nYoutube Channel ： <a href=\"http://youtube.com/user/dphkdphk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fuser%2Fdphkdphk&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b1e05240\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/user/dphkdphk</a><br />\nWebsite： <a href=\"http://www.dphk.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dphk.org&d=RosszpgqeMr9fazactANntr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f12f8bdc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dphk.org</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又分乜撚野享呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6682f953c0c50502654674e152f5d87677a72310","tid":496092,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T00:43:44.000Z","msg":"只有暴力先可以解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}